      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="shopping-bag"></i></div><h3>Order Booking</h3><p>Customers browse products, place orders, and make payments — all inside WhatsApp.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="message-square"></i></div><h3>Customer Support</h3><p>24/7 AI support that handles queries, complaints, and FAQs with human handoff when needed.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="megaphone"></i></div><h3>Broadcasting</h3><p>Send personalised bulk messages, offers, and updates with smart scheduling and analytics.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="credit-card"></i></div><h3>Payment Integration</h3><p>Accept UPI, cards, and wallets directly through WhatsApp with Razorpay and PhonePe.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="layout-dashboard"></i></div><h3>Dashboard & Analytics</h3><p>Track conversations, conversion rates, response times, and team performance in real time.</p></div>
