      <h2>WhatsApp AI <span class="heading-gradient">Questions</span></h2>
      <p>Common questions about our WhatsApp AI bot.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Do I need a WhatsApp Business API account?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We handle the entire WhatsApp Business API setup for you. You just need an active phone number. We take care of the rest — including WABA registration and template approval.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Can the AI send images, videos, and PDFs?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely. Our AI can send and receive images, videos, documents, PDFs, and location pins — whatever your business flow requires.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Does it work in multiple languages?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. The AI auto-detects the user's language and responds in Hindi, English, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, and more. Perfect for India's diverse customer base.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Can I transfer chats to a human agent?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. When the AI detects complex queries or customer frustration, it seamlessly transfers the conversation to a human agent with full chat history.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">How long does it take to set up?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Basic setup takes 24–48 hours. For custom workflows and integrations, most businesses are live within a week.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
